reviewText: I received the three cds and they do not work.  My review would be that I was not happy with my purchase. Thank you Kathleen

These are kinda boring.  I got the machine from a friend, but not the DVDs. They're ok, but nothing that I plan to do over and over again.  In fact, I think I'll be selling the whole system.  It is difficult to do these videos while staying on the machine correctly.  And again, they're just rather boring.

I was delighted to be able to find these DVD's at Amazon! They were not even available through Malibu Pilates. I received the original set when I purchased the Malibu Pilates Chair, but they had worn out with use, and I had just about given up hope of finding replacements when I located them on Amazon. Malibu Pilates, 3 DVDs Only
